  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 planted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3. Twelve of the thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; the 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor carries factorStatus 'not-assessed' because the assessment team concluded informally that the factor does not apply to a purely computational COU with no physical test article—an argument that belongs under factorStatus 'not-applicable' but was incorrectly encoded as 'not-assessed', leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
