    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that twelve of thirteen factors were assessed and that the unassessed 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor was informally judged inapplicable. The team did not recognise that leaving the factor not-assessed at MRL 3 constitutes a material epistemic gap under ASME V&V 40, and that the correct procedural path—documenting inapplicability under factorStatus 'not-applicable' with explicit justification—was not followed. The acceptance decision therefore rests on an incomplete credibility argument.",
